tafsir[8]{c,v,t}:
  14,11,"Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen jaabori …ďe: Ko goonga, men wonaali si wanaa …ďanndinke yeru mon. Ko woni tun, …óum hollaa hi…óen nannda e kala huunde. Alla no hertinira neeminirgol on Mo O muuyi e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, O su…ďoo e ma…ď…ďe Nulaa…ďe e yim…ďe …ďen. Menen, haananaa men nde men addanta on hujja mo …óa…ď…ďoton, si wanaa e duŇčayee Alla, men hattanaaka addugol …óum, ko Alla tun woni hattan…óo e …óum. Ko e Alla tun woni ko gom…óim…ďe …ďe Mo …ďen fawatoo e fiyakuuji ma…ď…ďe …óin fow."
  14,12,"Ko ha…óata men haa men he…ďa ngantu, wonoowo hakkunde e amen e fawagol Mo ngol? Gom…óii le O fewnirii men e laawol …ďurngol foccaade …ďannga. Pellet men mu√Ī√Īotoo e kon ko lorroton men e fennugol jalkita. Ko e Alla tun woni ko gom…óim…ďe …ďen fawatoo e denndaangal fiyakuuji ma…ď…ďe …óin."
  14,13,"Yeddu…ďe …ďen e yim…ďe Nulaa…ďe …ďen wi'i tuma …ďe ronkunoo wenjondirgol e Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen: Ma men yaltin on e saare amen, maa on yiltike e diina mon faade e diina amen. Alla wahayiniri e Nulaa…ďe …ďen √Īinnugol …ďe: Ma men halku too√Īu…ďe yeddi Alla e Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen."
  14,14,"Ma Men ho…ónu on, onon Nulaa…ďe …ďen e jokku…ďe on, e leydi ndin, …ďaawo nde …ďe halkaa. Kon ko jantaa e halkugol heefer…ďe fennoo…ďe …ďen, ho…óina Nulaa…ďe …ďen e gom…óim…ďe …ďen ka leydi …ďaawo halkeede …ďeya, …óum ko anndu…óo mawngu Am e ndeena Am e makko, o huli ko Mi kammbiranta mo lepte kon."
  14,15,"Nulaa…ďe …ďen …óa…ď…ďiri Joomi ma…ď…ďe walleede e ay…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen. Ontuma sooyi kala dunndaranke ∆īaggango goonga, salotoo…óo jokkude goonga si fee√Īanii mo."
  14,16,"√Ďalnde Darngal, on dunndarankeejo tawoyay Jahannama yesso makko, ka o waawataa laawaade. O yarniroyee e magge mbordi yim…ďe Yiite ndin ilayndi e ma…ď…ďe. ∆äum …óon…óitataa mo, o seerataa himo leptiree …óonka e kala noone e lepte."
  14,17,"Himo etoo yarugol …óam ndiyam tuma kala, kono o e…ď…ďataa mo…óugol …óam hakkee ko …óam metti …óam wuli luu…ďi. Maayde nden no ardana mo kala nokku, hakkee ko lepte …óen sattiri mo, kono le o maayataa sakko o fowtoo. Ko e …óum o heddotoo himo mee…óa lepte. Hara kadi lepte sattu…óe goo no habbitii mo yeeso."
  14,18,"Ko woni sifa golle …óe yeddu…ďe …ďen gollata immorde e sadaka, e mo∆ī∆īere, e yurmegol lo'u…ďe, ko wano ndoondi ndi henndu tii…ói e mun, e √Īalaande wippo- re; ndun henndu ronndora ndi ndoondi ndi henndu wutti e mbaadi sattundi, ndu saakita e kala nokku, haa batte mayri mula. Ko non golle heefer- …ďe …ďen wa'i, ko keeferaaku ngun wippotoo…óe, …ďe nafitoroytaa …óe √Ďalnde Darngal. ∆äen woni golle …óe tuuginaaki e gom…óinal, ko …óen woni majjere wo…ó…óunde laawol goonga ngol."